383
00:17:12,843 --> 00:17:14,167
 

384
00:17:14,167 --> 00:17:15,566
Je réfléchis encore.

385
00:17:15,566 --> 00:17:16,007
 

386
00:17:16,007 --> 00:17:19,795
Colonel, ce système solaire est
