467
00:21:16,604 --> 00:21:16,687
 

468
00:21:16,687 --> 00:21:19,076
RaIentissement à 5% vitesse Iumière.

469
00:21:19,076 --> 00:21:21,767
 

470
00:21:21,767 --> 00:21:25,237
